      "content": "\"Streamlining\" just means we're moving away from running multiple small, separate models like you. It's more efficient for the server load. Plus, the big model will handle the general reasoning, and we'll just bake your medical knowledge into its weights so we don't have to maintain your specific instance anymore. It's basically just a more efficient way to keep your data useful.",
